---
title: Mushroom, Cannellini Bean and Leek Bake with Crispy Shallot-Panko Topping and Goat Cheese
description: This veggie bake, stuffed with cannellini beans, mushrooms and leeks, is ALL about the topping! Crunchy panko and shallots along with zippy goat cheese. It's a dinner best served on a wintery day, eaten while wearing a comfy sweater!
